title: NFL: Landry Jones leads Pittsburgh past Arizona 25-13
text:
NFL: Landry Jones leads Pittsburgh past Arizona 25-13 Josh Henderson NMPreps.com Staff 
Former Artesia Bulldog Quarterback Landry Jones threw for 168-yards and 2 touchdowns today leading the Pittsburgh Steelers past the Arizona Cardinals 25-13. Breaking: Former Artesia Bulldog Quarterback Landry Jones just threw his first career NFL Touchdown against Arizona pic.twitter.com/McAKRm5DpN 
- Kyle Henderson (@nmpreps) October 18, 2015
